quote":{"pid":"ddadfdf853993493cf188d097cbef4d9b571c4c6","tid":668153,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T12:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kwsmgd6t\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkwsmgd6t&h=060e82db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暫時計到係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T12:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b1n6ty5g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb1n6ty5g&h=575694b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n更正"},{"pid":"8d4285ed9741d52da163079f5a6fce5bedb5a39f","tid":668153,"uid":111749,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T09:42:38.000Z","msg":"通常啲人係解完一次SE in SHO跟住再用啲result黎simplify, 未學過去non-dimensionalize會兜多幾步 不過逐步逐步黎:<br />\n<br />\n(1) 寫番好V(x)係咩黎先<br />\nV(x) = V_0*x^2/a^2=V_0 z^2 (z=ax is dimensionless), 其實即係harmonic oscillator potential energy, 用angular frequency黎表示<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/170053_b5e9b4f86ce43ca65bd79c894c4a924c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F170053_b5e9b4f86ce43ca65bd79c894c4a924c.gif&h=e0fa5d4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/170118_274a01ad7ad7ad7d73d5f0b399ae5db2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F170118_274a01ad7ad7ad7d73d5f0b399ae5db2.gif&h=efd7ae0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(2) 開始搞搞條SE<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/170648_068ae40523a24c9ef54edefd375e542d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F170648_068ae40523a24c9ef54edefd375e542d.gif&h=f5d0acbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係non-relativistic quantum physics入面既energy scale係<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/171137_8f173d0eaffc4b90c0c0361b8f37cc17.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F171137_8f173d0eaffc4b90c0c0361b8f37cc17.gif&h=26a7538f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以我地寫條SE做呢個form<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/171238_6a0fe32c3736658bde52846b7df05e01.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F171238_6a0fe32c3736658bde52846b7df05e01.gif&h=14f48fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住成條式除番個energy scale去non-dimensionalize佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/172207_bde7cf9049e122a728d29f2213bb2b67.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F172207_bde7cf9049e122a728d29f2213bb2b67.gif&h=b2effe93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為wavefunction本身係sqrt of probability density function, 冇dimension, 而z都係dimensionless, 所以成條式已經係dimensionless<br />\n<br />\n(3) 執靚佢<br />\n既然成條式係dimensionless, 每項既coefficient都係dimensionless, 咁你可以再轉一轉variables去執靚條式<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/173934_e746f170e2a60a973f6f1b2abdbfa5a7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F173934_e746f170e2a60a973f6f1b2abdbfa5a7.gif&h=77e4ce75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/172715_40af9ca5d4af4f53bc05e0396f2436f0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F172715_40af9ca5d4af4f53bc05e0396f2436f0.gif&h=13dd1f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住我叫番z'做z<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/172742_3019f422209a6593f02fad5560f36b79.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F172742_3019f422209a6593f02fad5560f36b79.gif&h=075a577b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nwhere<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/173948_575eda61e93c7ad9d05928580213fd9b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F173948_575eda61e93c7ad9d05928580213fd9b.gif&h=9feaf08e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於點解我地乘多個factor of 2係V_0同E前面, 其實係由solution of SE in SHO potential睇出黎, 因為wavefunction用呢個subsitution會俾番standard gaussian* hermite polynomial * normalization constants<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91fa09e9772bcd7ade5101edf4ead36537474ee4","tid":668153,"uid":111749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T09:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常啲人係解完一次SE in SHO跟住再用啲result黎simplify, 未學過去non-dimensionalize會兜多幾步 不過逐步逐步黎:<br />\n<br />\n(1) 寫番好V(x)係咩黎先<br />\nV(x) = V_0*x^2/a^2=V_0 z^2 (<span style=\"color: red;\">z=(x/a)</span> is dimensionless), 其實即係harmonic oscillator potential energy, 用angular frequency黎表示<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/170053_b5e9b4f86ce43ca65bd79c894c4a924c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F170053_b5e9b4f86ce43ca65bd79c894c4a924c.gif&h=e0fa5d4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/170118_274a01ad7ad7ad7d73d5f0b399ae5db2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F170118_274a01ad7ad7ad7d73d5f0b399ae5db2.gif&h=efd7ae0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(2) 開始搞搞條SE<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/170648_068ae40523a24c9ef54edefd375e542d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F170648_068ae40523a24c9ef54edefd375e542d.gif&h=f5d0acbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係non-relativistic quantum physics入面既energy scale係<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/171137_8f173d0eaffc4b90c0c0361b8f37cc17.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F171137_8f173d0eaffc4b90c0c0361b8f37cc17.gif&h=26a7538f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以我地寫條SE做呢個form<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/171238_6a0fe32c3736658bde52846b7df05e01.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F171238_6a0fe32c3736658bde52846b7df05e01.gif&h=14f48fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住成條式除番個energy scale去non-dimensionalize佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/172207_bde7cf9049e122a728d29f2213bb2b67.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F172207_bde7cf9049e122a728d29f2213bb2b67.gif&h=b2effe93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為wavefunction本身係sqrt of probability density function, 冇dimension, 而z都係dimensionless, 所以成條式已經係dimensionless<br />\n<br />\n(3) 執靚佢<br />\n既然成條式係dimensionless, 每項既coefficient都係dimensionless, 咁你可以再轉一轉variables去執靚條式<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/173934_e746f170e2a60a973f6f1b2abdbfa5a7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F173934_e746f170e2a60a973f6f1b2abdbfa5a7.gif&h=77e4ce75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/172715_40af9ca5d4af4f53bc05e0396f2436f0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F172715_40af9ca5d4af4f53bc05e0396f2436f0.gif&h=13dd1f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住我叫番z'做z<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/172742_3019f422209a6593f02fad5560f36b79.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F172742_3019f422209a6593f02fad5560f36b79.gif&h=075a577b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nwhere<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/173948_575eda61e93c7ad9d05928580213fd9b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F173948_575eda61e93c7ad9d05928580213fd9b.gif&h=9feaf08e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於點解我地乘多個factor of 2係V_0同E前面, 其實係由solution of SE in SHO potential睇出黎, 因為wavefunction用呢個subsitution會俾番standard gaussian* hermite polynomial * normalization constants<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nz=x/a先岩 打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}